{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e51578e105","title":"关于较重要外交复文的送审问题的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"673bcb556f","index":0,"year":1952,"month":9,"day":17,"articleId":"e51578e105"},{"id":"db706973e6","index":1,"year":1952,"month":9,"day":18,"articleId":"e51578e105"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"f65812ff0f","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"e51578e105","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"小平，即邓小平，当时任政务院副总理。"},{"id":"6275ad7734","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"e51578e105","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中央人民政府外交部1952年9月13日关于朝鲜拟派技术人员、技能者600余人来我国实习事给中国驻朝使馆的复电。复电表示，因我国各业各工厂生产繁忙，来人多安排有困难，以少派为宜。"},{"id":"965992a265","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"e51578e105","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"周，指周恩来。邓，指邓小平。"},{"id":"54b8401433","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"e51578e105","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"章汉夫，当时任中央人民政府外交部副部长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"d20c846699","type":"title","text":"关于较重要外交复文的送审问题的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"e51578e105"},{"id":"f65812ff0f","type":"paragraph","text":"小平同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"e51578e105"},{"id":"6275ad7734","type":"paragraph","text":"此电所说，与我们商定者不符。外交部发此电未先送审，请你查询告我为盼。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"e51578e105"},{"id":"965992a265","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"e51578e105"},{"id":"54b8401433","type":"paragraph","text":"九月十七日周、邓阅，送章汉夫时同志：","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"e51578e105"},{"id":"8be471bbba","type":"paragraph","text":"外交部最近有些较重要的外交复件未送中央审阅，对朝鲜的复电与中央的决策及我们面告朝鲜同志者不相符合，是不妥的。以后请加注意，除例行事务外，凡较重要的外交复文，均须送总理及我审阅之后，再行发出，以免出乱子。此事去年（或者是今年上半年？）有一次即告诉过你，要事不送审是不对的，你曾作了自我检讨，如何又忘记了","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"e51578e105"},{"id":"64d50ee354","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"e51578e105"},{"id":"1ef57d5a7e","type":"paragraph","text":"九月十八日","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"e51578e105"}],"page":{"id":"eab3a18600","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"e51578e105","start":251,"end":252}}}},"__N_SSG":true}